728955f-a.title: Richmond: Howard Avenue - Louis Street
728955f-a.text:
(1)
37 Howard Avenue, east side, seuth of Leuis Street, showing
the Jchn Martin residence. Here Maxim Gerky, womld renewned
Ruasian author, wrote his famous novel ''Mother' while staying
with the Martins, in 1906 (see ''The Sun'', Dec. 3, 1937). The
residence at one time belenged to Henry Sedley (1874 and 1898
maps).
June 18, 1926
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCEIONS.
(E)
The rear ef the house.
June 18, 1926.
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
The rear ef the house, leoking north.
June 18, 1926.
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
